reviewText:
Another great video in this series, demonstrating the use of the violet wand and some accessories.

Good safety procedure coverage and satisfying demonstration of technique.

My only complaints are that it could have been longer, and more information on finding or making the accessories would have been helpful.

Recommended for those interested in BDSM and electric play.
Pretty low on content, more about using the metallic rope along with the wand than anything else.
